+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${PKGSTEM} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

To avoid character encoding issues, ensure that you have your LC_CTYPE
environment set to one of the UTF-8 variants. E.g. en_US.UTF-8.
